{"lastModified":1755002171119,"uri":"c::7819143053::vessel::d5cbfb8b-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Gulet","Sailing"],"description":"Operating Area: Turkey\n\nLA BELLA VITA is the former CARPE DIEM IV, one of the most populare gulet in Turkey. She is a 47.00m / 154ft Luxury Gulet in mint conditions. Sleeping 12 guests in 6 cabins and with a crew of 7. The guest cabins comprise 2 master cabins, 2 double cabins, 1 twin cabin and 1 triple cabin, with a bed configuration of 4 king-sized, 1 queen-sized, and 3 double beds.\n\nCharters usually have a weekly rotation, boarding at 5pm, disembarkation at 10am but there is some flexibility according to the booking plan and charter duration.","blueprint":{"name":"LA BELLA VITA","images":["/media/media::image::c::7819143053::vessel::d5cbfb8b-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::69989f40-ad7a-11ef-9613-8bf31a54572e/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7819143053::vessel::d5cbfb8b-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::97bdfa00-ad7a-11ef-b72d-f7643baf70cd/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7819143053::vessel::d5cbfb8b-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::8b268eb0-ad7a-11ef-b72d-f7643baf70cd/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7819143053::vessel::d5cbfb8b-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::914c3240-ad7a-11ef-b72d-f7643baf70cd/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7819143053::vessel::d5cbfb8b-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::9f762470-ad7a-11ef-b72d-f7643baf70cd/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7819143053::vessel::d5cbfb8b-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::c162de80-d61a-11ee-bb53-c726cba6e4ba.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7819143053::vessel::d5cbfb8b-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::d60f3170-ad7a-11ef-afae-a7b965f4e2a2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7819143053::vessel::d5cbfb8b-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::d82f2b40-ad7a-11ef-afae-a7b965f4e2a2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7819143053::vessel::d5cbfb8b-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::d9b5