rtemis between 1999-2002, then on Tamomar 2 in 2002-200. He started working as Captain on gulet Monalisa in 2005, then on a private yacht 2009-2013. In 2013 became Captain aboard Tanomar. In 2021 he was Captain on gulet Bella Mare and, in 2022, he moved to La Bella Vita."},{"name":"Salih Akcan","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::7819143053::vessel::d5cbfb8b-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::7e6b3d20-ad79-11ef-acac-dbd8b11f5e6d/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"He worked as chef or patry chef in various restaurants around Bodrum before moving to M/Y Maia in 2021, to gullet Gazella in 2022, then on La Bella Vita. 3rd classified at chef competion during TYBA 2024."},{"name":"Oyku Yalcin","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::7819143053::vessel::d5cbfb8b-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::974def90-ad79-11ef-a562-a72676f038cb/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Previous work experiences in brief: She attended Piri Reis Maritime University, a private maritime upper education institution Ship cooking dept.) in Istanbul. She has been aboard since 2022."},{"name":"Aras Gulle","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::7819143053::vessel::d5cbfb8b-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::abb86050-ad79-11ef-a562-a72676f038cb/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Born in Izmir in 1988, Aras joined La Bella Vita crew in 2023. He takes care of clients because of his very fluent english. He also worked as chef on restaurant before embarking on yachts."},{"name":"Musa .","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::7819143053::vessel::d5cbfb8b-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::c527c260-ad79-11ef-8cc7-ad5e9cb427bd/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Born in 2001 in Fethiye. He started working on gulets since he was 16. He worked, before joining La Bella Vita on yacht Luce del Mare and Tersane 8. He take care of water sports and love fishing."},{"name":"Ege Akbukut","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::7819143053::vessel::d5cbfb8b-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::d6878b30-ad79-11ef-8cc7-ad5e9cb427bd/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"She's born in 2001. Ege has been hotel housekeepr until 2020, then she moved to the yachting industry, working on Gulet Bella Mare, before moving to La Bella Vita."},{"name":"Doğu Kaan Demirkol","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::7819143053::vessel::d5cbfb8b-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::0e3cb690-ad7a-11ef-bda3-e9c19453b7aa/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain"},{"name":"Koray Kilic","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::7819143053::vessel::d5cbfb8b-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::1c5347d0-ad7a-11ef-bda3-e9c19453b7aa/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Born in 1994 in Marmaris, Koray started wiìorking as deckhand on gulet Caferoglu 7 from 2011 to 2014. Then he worked as deckhand on Deniz Kizi and Grandemare (2016-2018). In 2020 he was captain on Sagapo and, in 2023 he was first officer on Bellamare. Very good sailor. "}],"pricing":{"weekPricingFrom":{"currency":"EUR","price":3850000,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":3850000,"unit":"WEEK"},"weekPricingTo":{"currency":"EUR","price":5600000,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":5600000,"unit":"WEEK"},"pricingInfo":[{"name":"October - May ","effectiveDates":[{"from":"2025-04-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2025-05-31T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2026-04-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2026-05-31T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2027-04-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2027-05-31T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2025-10-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2025-11-30T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2026-10-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2026-11-30T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2027-10-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2027-11-30T23:59:59.999Z"}],"pricing":{"currency":"EUR","charterFee":3850000,"inputAmountTaxed":"EXCLUSIVE","note":"","unit":"WEEK","lineItems":[{"item":"Charter Fee","quantity":1,"unitPrice":3850000,"amount":3850000,"taxRate":{"label":"VAT","value":0.2}},{"item":"APA","conditions":"","quantity":0.15,"unitPrice":3850000,"amount":577500}],"total":5197500,"subTotal":4427500,"totalTax":770000},"inclusionZones":[{"label":"Turkey","t